<h2 id="contact-the-press-office">Contact the press office</h2>

<p>You should only contact the press office if you have a media query or 
you’re a journalist.</p>

<p>You should contact the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/traffic-commissioners/about/access-and-opening">Office of the Traffic Commissioner</a> if you’re a member of the public with a general enquiry.</p>

<p>The press office cannot help with general enquiries from members of the public.</p>

<h2 id="resources-for-the-media">Resources for the media</h2>

<p>The following information is available on GOV.UK:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/announcements?departments%5B%5D=traffic-commissioners">our announcements</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?departments%5B%5D=traffic-commissioners">our publications</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/traffic-commissioners">the traffic commissioners</a></li>
</ul>
